item.description: Chicken is probably the most popular of all meat products. Best of the Best chicken.
item.content:encoded:
Chicken is probably the most popular of all meat products. Chicken is probably the most eaten and most loved non-vegetarian food product. This bird was probably domesticated in the very early centuries, after the nomadic man started settling down and domesticated animals for his benefit.

Interesting Facts

  • The human body can derive about 30 different nutritional substances from just 100 grams of chicken.
  • Just as the nutritional value of chicken is very high, so is the energy measure. 100 grams of this meat contains about 916 kilojoules of energy.
  • More than half the entrées ordered in fast food chains, hotels, motels, and restaurants are versions of fried chicken.
  • The chickens that are used to make soup products are known as “stewing hens”.
